[00:23.12] Life runs, trips, and gives no warning
[00:28.65] In the jeans pocket, the photo is what immobilizes me
[00:35.08] Time has no power under the light of that lamppost
[00:41.10] Loving is a cut, but it's what keeps us strong.
[00:48.76] Only the words bleed on these pages
[00:55.52] Where time froze our tears...
[01:00.69] Keep me in your chest, where the heart beats fast
[01:06.96] In the shine of the necklace, I am your luck!
[01:13.64] Wait for me, the way home is what's left
[01:20.09] Love is the baggage, the rest is just a party!
[01:29.73] (Oh, wait for me...)
[01:58.76] In the silence of the phone, your voice is the portal
[02:05.37] The world collapses, but here the embrace is real.
[02:11.58] Scars closed in paper and silver
[02:17.93] What is eternal, distance doesn't kill.
[02:25.24] Time stopped...
[02:28.21] Wait for me...
[02:31.32] In the paper shelter.